name: CI Munro Alternative Global Growth Fund
longDescription: The CI Munro Alternative Global Growth ETF (the Fund) seeks to generate risk-adjusted, absolute returns through exposure to global growth equities over the medium to long term, while maintaining a capital preservation mindset. The Fund will invest primarily in listed international equities, deploying a longshort equities strategy with a long bias. The investment strategy is designed to identify sustainable growth trends that are underappreciated and mispriced by the market, and the resulting winning and losing stocks.
